  "notes": "Fifth floor of the Olivine Lighthouse. The most item-rich floor: three visible item balls (Rare Candy, Super Repel, TM Swagger) and one hidden item (Hyper Potion via bg_event). Has two trainers: Sailor Ernest (3 Pokemon including 2 Machop and a Poliwhirl, spins randomly fast) and Bird Keeper Denis (Spearow/Fearow/Spearow, uses SPRITE_YOUNGSTER sprite). Denis's after-text and Ernest's seen-text both reference Cianwood, reinforcing the quest direction. The floor has 7 warp events: one staircase going up to 6F at (9,15), east stairs at (16-17,5) also going to 6F, and multiple paths going down to 4F. TM Swagger note: this is TM46 in the Japanese/international Gen 2 numbering."
